window.bookSummaryJSON = "The Cisco triplets are appalled by their widowed father's behavior. He seems to care more about his gold-digging fiancee than he does about his own son and daughters. Even worse, Dad put their spunky grandmother - head of the family candy company - in a nursing home against her will. Setting out to spring Granny Cisco, college seniors Sara, Hannah, and Sam soon prove that trouble comes in threes. Apparently, so does love... If everything goes according to plan, there's going to be quite a crowd at Granny's house come Christmas - and more proof than ever that there's no place like home for the holidays."; 
